Documentation.name: Compassion Technology
Documentation.notes: Compassion International Technology 07/22/2015 Added _Orchestration and _Workflow What Tool elements 07/15/2015 Added Phase and Status columns to PDM reports 07/10/2015 Fixed tool box sort order 07/10/2015 Added new elements requested by Dan Ducat 07/09/2015 Changed _ConsoleApp to Type Object 07/09/2015 Changed Zachman Stereotypes to "_..." 07/08/2015 Revised Zachman Stereotype Elements 07/01/2015 Added default size of system elements shape ( defSize(120,70); ) 06/30/2015 Improved System Elements 06/29/2015 Added System Elements 06/05/2015 Fill Color added to CICommonEntity 06/03/2015 Adde CICommonEntity 05/26/2015 Added CITransformationRule 04/29/2015 Changed type of FieldLength tagged value to 'String' from 'Integer' 04/20/2015 Added RoleTypeB Connector 04/16/2015 Added Type Elements 03/30/2015 Reordered Forms Tools 03/10/2015 Added CIPaperForm element 03/10/2015 Added CIFormAttribute stereotype 03/06/2015 Bug Fix to pick up deletes 03/04/2015 Improved 3 existing scripts and added script to do Physical to Logical attribute mapping 03/03/2015 Improved Physical Data Model Dictionary 02/25/2015 Testing Version 12 of Sparx 02/04/2015 Added Report: PDM_for_SFDC_Comparison - creates an unformatted spreadsheet that is then used to compare the PDM to SFDC 01/14/2015 Added Search: CI_FindCIDataAttribute_LogicalOrhpans - helps find CIDataAttributes that do not have a relationship to a logical attribute. Modified: Report: Physical_Data_Dictionary_Workbook - resolved FieldValues not populating when the DataType is something other then a Picklist. Modified: Report: Physical_Data_Model - resolved FieldValues not populating when the DataType is something other then a Picklist.

$Comment="This template is to convert the columns to ERD_Attributes." $Comment="Finding FK."
%if attOrderedMultiplicity==""% $fk=%list="Operation__FKParam" @separator=","% $search=%attName% $Comment="Temp fix - allow attribute creation for FKs" $Comment="$normalAtt=%FIND($fk, $search)%" $normalAtt="-1" %else% $normalAtt="-1" %endIf%
$Comment="*** (%attName%) (%attOrderedMultiplicity%) ($normalAtt) -"
%if $normalAtt=="-1"% Class { %TRANSFORM_REFERENCE(attName,attGUID)% name=%qt%%attName%%qt% stereotype="CIDataAttribute" scope="public" Tag { name = "attributeType" %if attOrderedMultiplicity==""% value = %qt%normal%qt% %else% value = %qt%primaryKey%qt% %endIf% } Tag { name = "commonDataType" value= "na" } Tag { name = "dbmsDataType" value=%qt%%attType%%qt% } Tag { name = "FieldLength" value=%qt%%attLength%%qt% } Tag { name = "Required" %if attAllowDuplicates==""% value = %qt%false%qt% %else% value = %qt%true%qt% %endIf% } %if attInitial!=""% Tag { name = "DefaultValue" value=%qt%%attInitial%%qt% } %endIf% } Association { %TRANSFORM_REFERENCE(attName,attGUID)% stereotype="CIDataConnector" Source { %TRANSFORM_REFERENCE(className,classGUID)% } Target { %TRANSFORM_REFERENCE(attName,attGUID)% } } %endIf%

RootTable.Filter: SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as CONCEPTUAL_OBJECT, T2.Name as RELATED_LOGICAL_OBJECT FROM (t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector ON (t_connector.End_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (t_connector.Start_Object_ID = T2.Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'CIDataConcept') AND (T2.Stereotype = 'ERD_Attribute') AND (t_connector.Connector_Type = 'Dependency')

SELECT D1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, D1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, D2.Name as PHYSICAL_DATA_ENTITY, D1.Name as PHYSICAL_DATA_ATTRIBUTE, C1.Connector_Type as CONNECTOR_TYPE, T1.Name as MESSAGE_NAME FROM (((t_object as D1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.End_Object_ID= D1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T1 ON (T1.Object_ID = C1.Start_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C2 ON (C2.End_Object_ID= D1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D2 ON (D2.Object_ID = C2.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'messageType') AND (D1.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute') AND (D2.Stereotype = 'CIDataElement') ORDER BY D2.Name, D1.Name, T1.Name

SELECT T3.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T3.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as PHYSICAL_OBJECT, T2.Name as TABLE_NAME, T3.Name as PHYSICAL_ATTRIBUTE, t_objectproperties.Value as DBMS_DATA_TYPE, A1.Name as COLUMN_NAME FROM ((((((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_xref as TX1 ON ((TX1.Client = T1.ea_guid) AND (TX1.Type = 'Transformation'))) LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON ((TX1.Supplier = T2.ea_guid) AND (T2.Stereotype = 'table'))) LEFT JOIN t_connector ON ((t_connector.Start_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID) AND (t_connector.Stereotype = 'CIDataConnector'))) LEFT JOIN t_object as T3 ON ((t_connector.End_Object_ID = T3.Object_ID) AND (T3.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute'))) LEFT JOIN t_objectproperties ON ((t_objectproperties.Object_ID = T3.Object_ID) AND (t_objectproperties.Property = 'dbmsDataType'))) LEFT JOIN t_xref as TX2 ON ((TX2.Client = T3.ea_guid) AND (TX2.Type = 'Transformation'))) LEFT JOIN t_attribute as A1 ON (TX2.Supplier = A1.ea_guid) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'CIDataElement') AND (t_objectproperties.Value is not null) AND (A1.Name is null) ORDER By T1.Name, T3.Name

select Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, ea_guid as CLASSGUID, name, problemnotes, t_objectproblems.status, t_objectproblems.DateReported from t_object join t_objectproblems on t_object.object_id = t_objectproblems.object_id order by name

SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as LOGICAL_OBJECT, T2.Name as LOGICAL_ATTRIBUTE, T2.Object_ID as LOGICAL_ATTRIBUTE_ID, T3.Name as PHYSICAL_ATTRIBUTE, T3.Alias as PHYSICAL_COLUMN, T3.Object_ID as PHYSICAL_ATTRIBUTE_ID, T4.Name as PHYSICAL_OBJECT, T4.Alias as PHYSICAL_TABLE, T4.Object_ID as PHYSICAL_OBJECT_ID FROM ((((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (T2.ParentID = T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (T2.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T3 ON (T3.Object_ID = C1.Start_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C2 ON (T3.Object_ID = C2.End_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T4 ON (T4.Object_ID = C2.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'ERD_Entity') AND (T2.Stereotype = 'ERD_Attribute') AND (C1.Connector_Type = 'Dependency') AND (T3.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute') AND (C2.Stereotype = 'CIDataConnector') AND (T4.Stereotype = 'CIDataElement') ORDER BY T1.Name, T2.Name, T2.Object_ID

SELECT D1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, D1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, D2.Name as LOGICAL_DATA_ENTITY, D1.Name as LOGICAL_DATA_ATTRIBUTE, C1.Connector_Type as CONNECTOR_TYPE, T1.Name as MESSAGE_NAME FROM (((t_object as D1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.End_Object_ID= D1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T1 ON (T1.Object_ID = C1.Start_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C2 ON (C2.End_Object_ID= D1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D2 ON (D2.Object_ID = C2.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'messageType') AND (D1.Stereotype = 'ERD_Attribute') AND (D2.Stereotype = 'ERD_Entity') ORDER BY D2.Name, D1.Name, T1.Name

SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T2.Name as LOGICAL_ENTITY_NAME, T1.Name as LOGICAL_ATTRIBUTE_NAME, T1.Note as ATTRIBUTE_NOTES FROM ((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector ON (T1.Object_ID = t_connector.End_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (T2.Object_ID = t_connector.Start_Object_ID)) WHERE (t_connector.Connector_Type = 'Association') AND (T1.Stereotype = 'ERD_Attribute') AND (T2.Stereotype = 'ERD_Entity') ORDER BY T2.Name, T1.Name

SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as MESSAGE_NAME, C1.Connector_Type as CONNECTOR_TYPE, D1.Name as LOGICAL_DATA_ATTRIBUTE, D2.Name as PHYSICAL_DATA_ATTRIBUTE FROM ((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.Start_Object_ID= T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D1 ON ((D1.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID) AND (D1.Stereotype = 'ERD_Attribute'))) LEFT JOIN t_object as D2 ON ((D2.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID) AND (D2.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute')) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'messageType') ORDER BY T1.Name

SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as RELATIONSHIP_NAME, T1.Object_ID as RELATIONSHIP_ID, T1.Note as RELATIONSHIP_NOTES, C1.Name as RELATIONSHIP_LABEL, T2.Name as RELATED_END_NAME, T2.Stereotype as RELATED_END_TYPE, C1.DestCard as CARDINALITY FROM (t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.Start_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (T2.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'ERD_naryAssociation') AND (C1.Connector_Type = 'Association') AND (T2.Stereotype IN ('ERD_Entity')) UNION SELECT T1.Object_Type, T1.ea_guid, T1.Name,T1.Object_ID, T1.Note, C1.Name, T2.Name, T2.Stereotype, C1.SourceCard FROM (t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.End_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (T2.Object_ID = C1.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'ERD_naryAssociation') AND (C1.Connector_Type = 'Association') AND (T2.Stereotype IN ('ERD_Entity')) ORDER BY RELATIONSHIP_NAME, RELATIONSHIP_ID

SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as MESSAGE_NAME, C1.Connector_Type as CONNECTOR_TYPE, D2.Name as LOGICAL_DATA_ENTITY, D1.Name as LOGICAL_DATA_ATTRIBUTE FROM (((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.Start_Object_ID= T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D1 ON (D1.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C2 ON (C2.End_Object_ID= D1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D2 ON (D2.Object_ID = C2.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'messageType') AND (D1.Stereotype = 'ERD_Attribute') AND (D2.Stereotype = 'ERD_Entity') ORDER BY T1.Name, D2.Name, D1.Name

SELECT T1.Object_Type as CLASSTYPE, T1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as MESSAGE_NAME, C1.Connector_Type as CONNECTOR_TYPE, D2.Name as PHYSICAL_DATA_ENTITY, D1.Name as PHYSICAL_DATA_ATTRIBUTE FROM (((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.Start_Object_ID= T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D1 ON (D1.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C2 ON (C2.End_Object_ID= D1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as D2 ON (D2.Object_ID = C2.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'messageType') AND (D1.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute') AND (D2.Stereotype = 'CIDataElement') ORDER BY T1.Name, D2.Name

SELECT C1.Connector_Type as CLASSTYPE, C1.ea_guid as CLASSGUID, T1.Name as START_ATTRIBUTE, T3.Name as START_ENTITY, C1.Name as RELATIONSHIP_NAME, T2.Name as END_ATTRIBUTE, T4.Name as END_ENTITY FROM (((((t_object as T1 LEFT JOIN t_connector as C1 ON (C1.Start_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T2 ON (T2.Object_ID = C1.End_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C2 ON (C2.End_Object_ID = T1.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T3 ON (T3.Object_ID = C2.Start_Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_connector as C3 ON (C3.End_Object_ID = T2.Object_ID)) LEFT JOIN t_object as T4 ON (T4.Object_ID = C3.Start_Object_ID) WHERE (T1.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute') and (T2.Stereotype = 'CIDataAttribute') AND (C1.Stereotype = 'CIDataConnector') AND (C2.Stereotype = 'CIDataConnector') AND (T3.Stereotype = 'CIDataElement') AND (C3.Stereotype = 'CIDataConnector') AND (T4.Stereotype = 'CIDataElement')
